      <h1 class='title'>Poverty</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 cc72-3WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_72ws' title='Col. 72WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c72WS' name='column_72ws' href='#column_72ws' rel='bookmark'>72WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-04970'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_365'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-battle' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_365' title='Link to this speech by Mr John Battle' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-john-battle" title="Mr John Battle">Mr. Battle</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-04970">To ask the Secretary of State for Work and Pensions how many children in Leeds, West have been lifted out of poverty since 1997. [132742]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-04971'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_366'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-chris-pond' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_366' title='Link to this speech by Mr Chris Pond' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-chris-pond" title="Mr Chris Pond">Mr. Pond</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-04971">The fifth annual 'Opportunity for all' report (Cm 5956) sets out the Government's strategy for tackling poverty and social exclusion and presents information on the indicators used to measure progress against this strategy.</p><a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_73ws' title='Col. 73WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c73WS' name='column_73ws' href='#column_73ws' rel='bookmark'>73WS</a><p id="S6CV0412P0-04972">Information in respect of Leeds West is not available, as data for these indicators goes down only to national or regional level. Below that, it would not be statistically robust.</p><p id="S6CV0412P0-04973">This publication is available in the Library.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
